  autocmd!
  autocmd FileType vim
                   \ setlocal foldmethod=expr |
                   \ setlocal foldexpr=VimFolds(v:lnum) |
                   \ setlocal foldtext=VimFoldText() |
                   " uncomment if you want see folds in the gutter
